@page "/basecoat"
<PageTitle>Tailwind / Basecoat - Saascade Docs</PageTitle>

<h1>Tailwind / Basecoat</h1>

<main class="documentation">

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Overview</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Basecoat is a Tailwind CSS component library offering a clean,
            minimal design system for Saascade components.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>Setup</h3>

        <pre><code>builder.Services.AddSingleton&lt;IDesignSystem&gt;(DesignSystems.Tailwind.Basecoat);</code></pre>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Comparison with DaisyUI</h2>

        <p>
            Basecoat provides a different aesthetic compared to DaisyUI while using the
            same Tailwind utility foundation. Choose based on your design preferences.
        </p>

    </section>

</main>
